## BYOK Encryption
```python
from utils.encryption import encrypt_api_key, decrypt_api_key, validate_gemini_api_key

encrypted = encrypt_api_key(plaintext_key)    # before DB storage
plaintext = decrypt_api_key(encrypted_key)    # before use in agents
is_valid  = validate_gemini_api_key(api_key)  # validate format before saving
```
Stored in `users.gemini_api_key_encrypted` (TEXT).

**LLM cache invalidation on key change**: When a user updates or deletes their BYOK key, invalidate all cached LLM responses for that user. Otherwise the new key may receive results generated under the old key.

```python
from utils.cache import invalidate_user_llm_cache

await invalidate_user_llm_cache(str(user_id))  # call after set and delete
```

Key management endpoints:
```
GET    /api/v1/profile/api-key/status   # has key?
POST   /api/v1/profile/api-key          # save/update
DELETE /api/v1/profile/api-key          # delete
POST   /api/v1/profile/api-key/validate # validate before saving
```
